column2: SELECT dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#, #) AS n,   dbo.fCosmoComovDist2ObjectsRADEC(#,#,#,photoz,pra,pdec,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT) AS n1,   n.objID, n.distance, n.type,   p.ra AS pra, p.dec AS pdec, p.modelmag_r,   pz.z as photoz FROM Galaxy AS G   LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON n.objid=p.objid   LEFT JOIN Photoz as pz ON n.objid=pz.objid   WHERE G.objID = n.objID INTO MyDB.NearbyObjEq5
